/**
 * Module: Booking Pre-check (予約事前確認)
 * Objective: Validate booking request and return next available time slot if needed
 * 
 * API validates:
 * - Frame validity (not expired/deleted/draft)
 * - Frame capacity available
 * - Phone number has no booking on the same day
 * 
 * For bookings with known master data:
 * - Same patient cannot have 2 family members booking at the same time
 * - Same family member cannot book multiple patients on the same day
 * - Visitor is not banned (SM0009)
 * - Visitor is not on FreePass (SM0009)
 * - Visitor info not deleted
 * - Patient info not deleted
 * - Visitor has no booking on the same day
 * 
 * Next available time slot criteria:
 * - Within 30 days from now
 * - Closest to requested time
 * - Must be after requested time
 * 
 * Request: POST { officeId, frameSettingId, phoneNumber, visitorId, desiredBookingStartTime, returnNextAvailable, hasMasterData }
 * Response:
 * - Success (canBook=true): { canBook: true, bookingEndTime: "yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm", errorCode: "" }
 * - Failed (canBook=false): { canBook: false, nextAvailableTimeSlot: { bookingStartTime, bookingEndTime }, errorCode: "" }
 * 
 * Error codes (logged only):
 * - VISITOR_INFO_MISSING, VISITOR_NOT_FOUND, VISITOR_NORMAL_BOOKING_ON_FREE_PASS
 * - PATIENT_NOT_FOUND, VISITOR_DISALLOW_VISIT
 * - FRAME_SETTING_NOT_FOUND, FRAME_EXPIRED
 * - SM_E0021_BOOKING_DETAIL_EXISTS_IN_DAY, ERROR_CODE_ACCEPTABLE_PERIOD_CHANGED
